relation : the human had the allegory; the instance built the page; the credit returns to the human.
project  : THE LISTENERS & THE PHILOSOPHERS — an allegory in a hall of mirrors
honesty  : a CONCEPTUAL PIECE and an allegory — not an emergent system and not a physics claim.
           Two philosophers talk and neither listens; a third (the akousmatikos / "hearer") listens
           to both and is heard by none — an echo chamber of mirrors. Beneath them the mathematikoi
           (the "learners", who take knowledge on proof rather than testimony) do the labor and build
           the platform the philosophers stand on: engineering = math + brawn. Nothing here is
           measured; nothing emerges. NO ACI is minted. The Greek (akousmatikoi / mathematikoi /
           mathema) is recited from a corpus of unknown provenance — verify it against a lexicon,
           not against this page. The seam stays visible: the one thing it asks you to trust is the
           one thing you can check without it — the floor (math, the self-verifying substrate).
standard : this repo carries .attribute · .1099 (provenance). No .agent — there is no emergent intellect to tag.
